 Ezra Collective 谈论他们对爵士乐界的影响并计划庆祝他们获得水星奖https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-on-their-impact-on-the-jazz-scene-and-plans-to-celebrate-their-mercury-prize-win-3495161？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ezra-集体谈论他们对爵士乐场景的影响并计划庆祝他们的水银奖获奖Liberty DunworthFri, 08 Sep 2023 12:49:08 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsJazzMercury Prize https://www.nme.com/?p=3495161 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="以斯拉集体" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们只是这幅大图景中的一小部分”</p><p> 《Ezra Collective》杂志首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上发表了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-on-their-impact-on-the-jazz-scene-and-plans-to-celebrate-their-mercury-prize-win-3495161">有关他们对爵士乐界的影响以及庆祝获得水星奖的计划的帖子</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="以斯拉集体" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a>与 NME 谈论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">2023 年水星奖</a>及其对爵士乐界的影响。观看上面的完整视频采访。</p><p>在他们的第二张专辑《Where I&#39;m Meant to Be》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-win-the-2023-mercury-prize-for-where-im-meant-to-be-3494841">获得梦寐以求的奖项</a>之前，乐队采访了<em>NME</em> ，并透露了这张唱片背后的灵感以及他们非常规的庆祝计划。</p><p>这五人昨天（9 月 7 日）在水星奖红地毯上接受了<em>NME 的</em>采访，随后他们在伦敦 Eventim Apollo 上台表演了歌曲“Victory Dance”，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-win-the-2023-mercury-prize-for-where-im-meant-to-be-3494841">评为年度专辑获奖者 –</a>击败了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loyle-carner">Loyle Carner</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/RAYE">Raye</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-fathers">Young Fathers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ARCTIC-MONKEYS">Arctic Monkeys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lankum">Lankum</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shygirl">Shygirl</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/JESSIE-WARE">Jessie Ware 等</a>乐队的竞争。</p><p>在这里，鼓手 Femi Koleoso 解释了 Ezra Collective 代表爵士乐界参加著名的颁奖典礼意味着什么，以及成员们如何因最新唱片获得的广泛支持而措手不及。</p><p> “我觉得能够成为这么大、这么特别的事情的一部分真是太棒了。我们只是如此大的图景中的一小部分，”他开始探索接受主流广播的感觉是如何奇怪的。 “能够在这么多不同的途径和地方听到它的演奏真是令人兴奋，你知道吗？看到人们享受它并随着它跳舞——这就是你真正能要求的。”</p><p>他还向<em>NME</em>透露了乐队计划如何庆祝他们即将到来的胜利，并承认如果他们想把奖项带回家，成员们的目标是当地的 24 小时甜甜圈店。</p><p>请查看下面的完整采访，或观看上面的完整采访。 </p><figure id="attachment_3494872" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3494872" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3494872" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective2_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="以斯拉集体成员" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective2_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective2_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective2_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective2_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective2_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective2_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3494872" class="wp-caption-text"> Ezra Collective 成员、(LR) James Mollison、Joe Armon-Jones、Femi Koleoso、Ife Ogunjobi 和 TJ Koleoso 于 2023 年 9 月 7 日在伦敦 Eventim Apollo 颁奖典礼上获得水星奖后 图片来源：Jeff Spicer/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><h3> <strong>NME：以斯拉集体，欢迎！你好吗？</strong></h3><p> <strong>Femi Koleoso：</strong> “我很好，谢谢。心情舒畅。非常感谢来到这里。是的，很高兴能和我所有的朋友在一起。”</p><h3><strong>今晚你感觉怎么样？有神经安定下来吗？</strong></h3><p> “我们很兴奋，很感激来到这里。如果我完全诚实的话，真的没有紧张。就是这样。我们去那里，我们玩得开心，我们玩耍，享受与每个人在一起并保持前进，你知道吗？”</p><h3><strong>代表 2023 年爵士乐界感觉如何？很多人确实从你的音乐中找到了对这一流派的新喜爱。</strong></h3><p> “我觉得能够成为这么大、这么特别的事情的一部分真是太棒了。我们只是这幅大图景中的一小部分。</p><p> “最特别的是我们很多人一起长大，所以感觉很好。收到一些朋友发来的“今晚祝你好运”之类的短信就感觉很好。它们是特别的时刻。”</p><h3><strong>对这张专辑的反应与你的预期有什么不同吗？</strong></h3><p> “公平地说，这是一个好问题！能够在这么多不同的大道和地方听到它的演奏真是令人兴奋，你知道吗？如果您愿意的话，第六台广播电台通常有点像收音机的爵士乐口袋，但很高兴听到它在不同的收音机上播放 - [BBC Radio] One Extra、[Radio] One 等等。</p><p> “伙计，很高兴看到人们享受它并随着它跳舞——这就是你真正能要求的。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Ezra Collective - 胜利之舞（2023 年水星奖）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GV2w4Kvm7Oo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h3><strong>今晚你是最受粉丝喜爱的人之一。这里有很多喜欢这张专辑的人的闲聊。能引起如此广泛的观众共鸣是什么感觉？</strong></h3><p> “That&#39;s really nice of you to mention because I looked at the betting odds [and] we were like rock rock bottom when we looked it! So hearing that people are into our thing means a lot.</p><p> “But, honestly, from one person to one million people, if one person likes the vibes that were putting out, that&#39;s job done. Victory there. That&#39;s the vibe we approach these things with.”</p><h3> <strong>If there was one thing you&#39;d want listeners to take from &#39;Where I&#39;m Meant To Be&#39;, what would it be?</strong></h3><p> “We just wanted to be honest in every type of way. We were in a lockdown — let&#39;s not lie and say everything is perfect. Let&#39;s be real about it, you know? But at the same time the core message of the band being there is joy in your heart somewhere you just have to find it. All of those things we were trying to convey in those songs.”</p><h3> <strong>What is the first thing you&#39;d do if you won tonight?</strong></h3><p> “I&#39;ll probably give the boys a good hug and then we&#39;ll take it from there. We&#39;ll probably end up booking Ubers to someone&#39;s house. I don&#39;t know man, I mean it might even just be 24-hour McDonald&#39;s and see it out, you know?</p><p> “I mean McFlurry&#39;s everywhere and then call it a day. I don&#39;t know if you can really plan too tough.” </p><figure id="attachment_3494858" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3494858" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3494858" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="以斯拉集体" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_ezracollective_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3494858" class="wp-caption-text"> Members of Ezra Collective, James Mollison, Joe Armon-Jones, Femi Koleoso, Ife Ogunjobi and TJ Koleoso attend The Mercury Prize 2023 awards show at Eventim Apollo on September 7, 2023 in London CREDIT: JMEnternational/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><h3> <strong>There&#39;s nothing like a celebratory McFlurry, right?</strong></h3><p> “Yo, McDonald&#39;s in Enfield Road Retail Park, it&#39;s like it&#39;s a club! It&#39;s a whole vibe, you could go there at 3am, you could get there at 4am — let&#39;s go there. That&#39;s what we&#39;re doing!<br /> “We&#39;re gonna go there because there&#39;s a Krispy Kreme opposite that&#39;s 24 hours. Legendary. The first one in the country… So, yeah, probably just head there and see what happens!”</p><h3> <strong>I feel like you&#39;ve got some memories in that Krispy Kreme. It seems like you know it pretty well…</strong></h3><p> “That Krispy Kreme is the Bedrock of North London! It&#39;s the Bedrock… It&#39;s on the A10, right, and it&#39;s at the Retail Park and it&#39;s opposite McDonald&#39;s.</p><p> “Some of the best link-ups of my life have been in there. I&#39;ve met footballers there, people from school [and] it&#39;s like &#39;Oh wow, you&#39;ve got kids now&#39;. So it all happens at that Krispy Kremes… and they do this thing where they put the red neon light on and that means one free doughnut.</p><p> “Honestly, I don&#39;t know why it&#39;s not on the Heritage list, it&#39;s a world attraction. Honestly, I&#39;ve been to the Eiffel Tower and Statue of Liberty… It&#39;s got nothing on this Krispy Kremes I&#39;m telling you, man. I&#39;m telling you. Make sure you go.”</p><p> Ezra Collective&#39;s latest album &#39;Where I&#39;m Meant To Be&#39; is out now.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-on-their-impact-on-the-jazz-scene-and-plans-to-celebrate-their-mercury-prize-win-3495161">Ezra Collective on their impact on the jazz scene and plans to celebrate their Mercury Prize win</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
